context: Sunday blessings to all! 😍🙏 Let us embrace this day with gratitude and reflect on the words of Psalm 118:24 - "This is the day that the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it."
This is the day that the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it. Good morning! Today is a new day and a new opportunity to rejoice and be glad. Make the most of it!
This is the day that the LORD has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it. Explore the depths of God's Word every day and today. Have a good day!

Rejoice in the #FridayFeeling! reminds us, "This is the day that the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it." Embrace the gift of today, spreading love and kindness wherever you go. Let your light shine bright! 😍🙌 ❤️
This is the day that the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it. Praying you have a blessed Sunday worshipping the Lord with your church family ❤️
Good morning people of God! Thank you Lord for another day to praise you - ❌ 😍 😍 "This is the day that the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it."

This is the day that the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it. Sunday is a day for self-reflection and prayer. Enjoy your Sunday and spend time to refuel your soul and reflect on your blessings while planning for a productive week ahead. #SpiritualSunday

This is the day that the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it! Have a great week everybody - Choose Joy, choose Peace, choose to Love & Be Kind - Help where ever You can & be good to yourself and to those you cross path with!
This is the day that the LORD has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it. HAPPIEST BIRTHDAY PING DALMACIO @iamgnip GOD BLESS YOU MORE!!! 😍🙏 😍 🌌 ❤️

HELLO TUESDAY! "This is the day that the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it." You're filled with overflowing & uncontainable joy, you walk in the power of the Holy Spirit, because you're abundantly helped. Amen! Do have a Great Tuesday!
Good morning everyone!!! Enjoy your Sunday. This is the day that the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it! Low key Day for me.

Happy Sunday Fam. Good Morning Heavenly Father and thank you for another day! For this is the day that the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it! Father I pray that the meditation of every heart, and the praise of every lip be pleasing to you today. In Jesus' name amen.

Good morning, frens! Rise and shine. It's Sunday. This is the day that the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it! Have a blessed day full of so much hope, anything negative will retreat upon seeing you!

Good morning, beloved ones! Psalm 118:24 declares that this is the day that the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it. This is your season to embrace joy, success, contentment, and happiness. Celebrate each moment, for blessings abound. Rejoice, for you are loved. 🌌🌞 😍

There are two great days in a person's life-the day we are born & the day we discover why. Celebrating your birthday means you just don't get older, you exactly get better 😍🙏 "This is the day that the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it."
This is the day that the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it. Be blessed all of you my family of friends! You are treasured!

Today is Sunday. "This is the day that the LORD has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it." Let these profound words resonate within your very being. Embrace the truth that each day is a precious gift lovingly bestowed upon us by our Heavenly Father, brimming with opportunity for joy, growth and boundless gratitude. Blessed sunday.

Grace-filled Sunday! This is the day that the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it! Thank You Lord for the community who has weathered the storms and remain strong and purposeful! Be blessed

Happy Sunday 🌌🌞 May this blessed day fill our heart with renewed hope and inspire us to walk in faith. Remember, as the Psalmist wrote: This is the day that the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it.
This is the day that The LORD has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it. ~Psalm 118:24 . Have an amazing day everyone! 🌌🌤️

Wishing everyone a blessed Sunday filled with joy, peace, love and divine favor! May your day be illuminated by the Word of God , uplift your spirit: "This is the day that the LORD has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it." ✨ 😍🙏 ❌ #SundayBlessings #JoyfulHeart

The Bible says: This is the day that the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it. That is a great gift that God gives us! Thank you God for your great love! Let's all enjoy together in harmony and meditate on the word of God! 😍🙌 ❤️ 🌌 😍😍

Good Sunday morning! Embrace this day with gratitude and joy. Psalm 118:24: "This is the day that the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it." May your day be blessed and filled with worship. Have a wonderful Sunday! 🌌🌞 😍🙏
Good morning Patriots ☕ Happy Memorial Day weekend🌌🌌 Enjoy your day with faith and love. "This is the day that the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it."
Nothing but the light splashing of the waves, the doves, and a few other birds saying Good Morning. "This is the day that the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it." Rejoice - choose joy

Happy #BlessedFriday! May your day be filled with the joy and grace of the Lord. "This is the day that the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it." Remember, His love and blessings are everlasting. Have a blessed weekend ahead! 😍🙏🌌 ❤️

Happy Friday! "This is the day that the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it." Our time is limited. Let's rejoice in each day we get, in every aspect of who we are, & in everything that we do have as precious gifts from God! GOD LOVES YOU!! ❤️ #God

This is the day that the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it. Welcome to Koinonia! Get ready for an outpouring of healing, restoration and encounter with God. Open up your heart to receive all that He has in store for you. Enjoy this wonderful day!
Good morning Patriots and Friends! This is the day that the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it! Have an awesome Saturday!!! 🌌🌌🌌🌌🌌🌌 ❌ ❌ ❌ 😍🙏🌌 😍🙏🌌 😍🙏🌌 🌌 🌌 🌌

Happy Month to you all. "This is the day that the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it." May joy and happiness fill your hearts. Together, let's create moments worth cherishing and spread love, peace and joy. Jesus loves you!
